cz.ive.process
Interface ProcessExecution

All Known Implementing Classes:
Exchange.RendezvousExecution, ProcessExecutionImpl, Say.SayExecution
public interface ProcessExecution

Embodies process execution. ProcessTemplate can store information needed per process execution here.

Author:
Ondra

getParameters

java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object> getParameters()
Retrieves parameters of this process. Parameters are process specific data that elaborates meaning of the process. It is used to distinguish between slightly different processes from one process familly (for example speech)

parameters of this process execution
